  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd6\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Complaint to the Singapore Attorney General to arrest Gota",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign media reported that a group of lawyers from the International Truth and Justice Project (ITJP) filed a complaint with the Attorney General of Singapore demanding the immediate arrest of former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa.",
        "The complaint has been filed alleging that former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa committed war crimes in violation of the Geneva Convention when he was the Defense Secretary.",
        "The 63-page complaint alleges violations of the Geneva Conventions, international humanitarian law and international criminal law during the 2009 LTTE conflict."
      ],
